Merge pull request #15 from ewrogers/feature/filter-scripting
feat: debug filters
feat: network packet builder and serialization
properly select next available skill in skilltrainer ui when skill learned
prevent null reference when pooling ability effects and source has despawned
allow cutscenes activated by non player triggers such as blocks to work in offline mode
prevent null reference when unitialized unitcontroller enters trigger
don't add saved status effects that are zone dependent when loading game
fixed issue with quest prerequisites not recognizing the current step properly
fix issue with icons showing full cooldown when mounted
further logic fixes for despawn ability effect objects
fix ability effect destruction logic to prevent dictionary duplicate key error
allow unit spawn node to parent the units it spawns
allow non repeatable behaviors to play in cutscenes since the cutscene itself could be repeatable
prevent null reference from showing minimap icon when player not spawned
add event triggers and check interactable choice name for use interactable objective and trigger
allow control of unit spawn nodes with cutscene signals
fix UMA white dress and fade material
prevent null reference when a behavior tries to reset state when it wasn't triggered by a player
prevent null reference when no movement audio loop is available
feat: add behavior for better scroll to index
feat: bit flags for larger values
feat: add copy to json button
feat: support text views and computed properties
feat: remember last known position and size
feat: add console severity label and context menu
